# HostelPro — Hostel Management System

A comprehensive MERN stack hostel management system built for managing rooms, residents, billing, and maintenance.

## 🔗 Live Demo
- **Frontend:** https://hotelmanagmen.netlify.app
- **Backend API:** https://hotel-managment-agx7.onrender.com

## 🔑 Test Credentials
| Role | Email | Password |
|------|-------|----------|
| Admin | admin@hostelpro.com | admin123 |
| Staff | staff@hostelpro.com | staff123 |
| Resident | resident@hostelpro.com | res123 |

## ✨ Features
- JWT Authentication with role-based access (Admin, Staff, Resident)
- Room Allocation with real-time floor grid view
- Resident Management with check-in/checkout
- Maintenance Request tracking and assignment
- Billing and Invoice generation with payment recording
- Financial Reports with charts and graphs
- User Role management and permissions
- Notifications system

## 🛠 Tech Stack
| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React 18, Vite, TailwindCSS, Recharts |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas |
| Auth | JWT + bcrypt |
| Deployment | Netlify + Render |

## 🚀 Run Locally

### Backend
```bash
cd server
npm install
npm run dev
# Server runs on http://localhost:5000
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd client
npm install
npm run dev
# App runs on http://localhost:5173
```

